ent\"><code>HTMLParagraphElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLPictureElement\"><code>HTMLPictureElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLPreElement\"><code>HTMLPreElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLProgressElement\"><code>HTMLProgressElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLQuoteElement\"><code>HTMLQuoteElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLScriptElement\"><code>HTMLScriptElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSelectElement\"><code>HTMLSelectElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement\"><code>HTMLShadowElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSourceElement\"><code>HTMLSourceElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLStyleElement\"><code>HTMLStyleElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCaptionElement\"><code>HTMLTableCaptionElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableCellElement\"><code>HTMLTableCellElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableColElement\"><code>HTMLTableColElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code></strong> インターフェイスは、 JavaScript の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> が拒否されたときにグローバルスクリプトコンテキストに送信されるイベントを表します。</span>これらのイベントは、測定やデバッグ目的に使用すると特に有益です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"コンストラクター","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"promiserejectionevent\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent/PromiseRejectionEvent\" title=\"PromiseRejectionEvent()\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>指定したパラメータで <code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> イベントを生成する。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>親である <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> のプロパティも継承しています。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"promiserejectionevent.promise\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent/promise\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent.promise</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd>拒否された JavaScript の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"promiserejectionevent.reason\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent/reason\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent.reason</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise/reject\"><code>Promise.reject()</code></a> に渡される Promise が拒否された理由を示す値、または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>このインターフェイスには固有のメソッドはありません。親である <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a> からメソッドを継承しています。</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"events","title":"イベント","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"rejectionhandled\"><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/rejectionhandled\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">rejectionhandled</a></code></dt>\n <dd>JavaScript の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> が拒否され、promise の reject イベントハンドラーのコードが実行された後に発生する。</dd>\n <dt id=\"unhandledrejection\"><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/unhandledrejection\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">unhandledrejection</a></code></dt>\n <dd>reject に対するイベントハンドラーがない状態で JavaScript の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> が拒否されたときに発生する。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onunhandledrejection</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>reason<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#promiserejectionevent\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">PromiseRejectionEvent の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PromiseRejectionEvent","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onrejectionhandled</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onunhandledrejection</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"コンストラクター","id":"constructor"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"},{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"イベント","id":"events"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの対応","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"PromiseRejectionEvent インターフェイスは、 JavaScript の Promise が拒否されたときにグローバルスクリプトコンテキストに送信されるイベントを表します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PromiseRejectionEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"PromiseRejectionEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/promiserejectionevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/promiserejectionevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent","title":"PromiseRejectionEvent"}],"pageTitle":"PromiseRejectionEvent - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}